  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Passenger travel to the EU by air, rail or sea after Brexit
  </h1>
</div>

  </div>
  
  <div class="column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    What you may need to do to travel to or in the EU and EEA after the UK leaves the EU on 12 April 2019.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

